Pauline and Paulette;;81;;84;;PG;;A delightfully bittersweet story of four elderly sisters and their relationship with each other. For Pauline (Dora van der Groen), life is simple. She lives with Martha (Julienne De Bruyn), the eldest of her four sisters, in a small town between Brussels and the seacoast. When Martha suddenly dies, everyone's world is turned upside down. Neither Paulette (Ann Petersen) or their youngest sister Cecile (Rosemarie Bergmans), feel they can be responsible for caring for their sister.;;Drama,Comedy;;Lieven Debrauwer;;2002;;Dora van der Groen,Ann Petersen,Rosemarie Bergmans,Idwig Stephane,Julienne De Bruyn,Fran√ßois Beukelaers,Nand Buyl;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/pauline_and_paulette